I have found a file called error_log in my sites root folder containing previous PHP and MySQL errors, so error logging is already working.&nbsp; But I want to understand how and why its working.
&nbsp;
I checked my php.ini file:

error_reporting = E_ALL &#38; ~E_NOTICE

display_errors = On

display_startup_errors = Off..." />
		
		
		
