<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>should be&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span  style="font-family:'courier new', courier, monospace;">function my_error_log($error_t<strong><span  style="color:#ff0000">e</span></strong>xt)</span></p>
</div>
